@node "BBIntro" "Introduction"
@prev "Main"
 @{b}@{u}@{fg shine}Introduction@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}

 BancaBase  is  a  tool  for  family  budget  and current account management.
 During  developement,  particular  attention  has  been  paid to the ease of
 use in order to keep it usable  by  everyone,  including  those  with  small 
 informatic knowledge.

 However  this  doesn't  mean  few  options  or lack of possibilities.  After
 having  properly understood the concepts used by this program, you will find
 that possibilities are many and all easy to access.

 This manual is only intended as a reference guide for correct program usage.
@endnode

@node "BBCopyRights" "CopyRights and Information"
@prev "Main"
  @{b}@{u}@{fg shine}CopyRight and Information@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}

  B A N C A B A S E   III   V 1.3a

  (C) 1994/97 by @{"Stefano Dardari" link "BBAuthor" 0} Rimini

 The  program,  the  whole  of  parts that make up the configurable graphical
 interface,   general  layout,  archive  structures  and  anything  is  about
 BancaBase has been designed by @{"Stefano Dardari" link "BBAuthor" 0}.

 The  program  has  been written in 'C' using SAS/C++ 6.57 © by SAS Institute
 Inc.  Cary NC USA.  I wish to remind that in no case the author (myself) can
 be  held  responsible  for  any  damage  or  error  directly  or  indirectly
 consequential to the use (or misuse) of this program.

 Products  and trademarks quoted into this document are registered trademarks
 belonging to the respective companies and/or authors.

 This  program  is  @{"ShareWare" link "BBShareWare" 0}.  For further details
 please refer to the appropriate section of this document.
@endnode

@node "BBAuthor" "Contacting the Author"
@prev "Main"

 @{b}@{u}@{fg shine}Conctating the Author@{ub}@{uu}@{fg text}

 You can contact me at the following addresses:


 EMail    : @{b}sdardari@rimini.com@{ub}

 FidoNet  : @{b}2:332/301.200@{ub}


 or by conventional mail at the address:

      @{b}Stefano Dardari

      via Romagna 15

      47900 Rimini RN

      Italy@{ub}


 I use to answer to everyone, but it's important not to be in a hurry ! :)

 Generally  I  manage to answer EMails within few days, Fidonet within one or
 two weeks, conventional mails ...  I can't tell !  :)

 If  you  own  an EMail address or know some friend who can send messages for
 you this means is preferable (for you too).

 Please  contact  me  exclusively for reasons concerning this program (or the
 others  I  have  written).   A  lot  of people use to ask everything without
